LuCI gettext catalogs for luci-app-glinet-privacy
==================================================

- templates/glinet_privacy.pot — template (regenerated; do not edit by hand except to fix tooling)
- <lang>/glinet_privacy.po — per-language catalog (edit msgstr lines)

Regenerate POT and refresh PO stubs from the repository root:

  python tools/extract-luci-i18n-strings.py
  python tools/i18n-build-po-from-pot.py

Then translate empty msgstr entries in po/uk/, po/de/, etc. English (po/en/) uses msgstr = msgid.

**Runtime catalogs:** `install.sh` (default) installs Lua sources only (English UI if no `.lmo` on the device). To ship translations, run **`po2lmo`** from OpenWrt/LuCI host tools (same as upstream LuCI packages) and copy **`glinet_privacy.<lang>.lmo`** to **`/usr/lib/lua/luci/i18n/`** on the router.
